text: Nabiyow tohuk lakal ama korosuk ixxic: Nabii Muusah Tawraat kitab necee tama kay diinih marak taama yessemeqqe marah niqmat duudusiyyah, ken diinih caagiidak kulliimih Baxxaqqaa kee israa-iil xayloh tirtoo kee Racmatta yakke kitaaba usun Rabak lakal ugut yaniih sinni Rabbit yangoorowoonu waanam nummaysaanamkeh
